name: In the middle of nowhere 2
description:
Same day, same filling.Almost 4 months away from home more than 6000 km. our trade line was from Malaysia through Singapore, Indonesia and some ports at Papua New Guinea. I am still a deck cadet. It’s a practice position on board a vessel. Assisting to everyone from day to day, learning plenty new information time running as a rocket from airport departure to coming back at home. Middle of my contract passed, nice crew around me and hundred miles of sea all round me. Every day You have a time to think about everything, every day you growing as a man.
No any postproduction made on this picture. Feel this freedom with me.
